<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/aftoc.html" class="external text" title="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/aftoc.html" rel="nofollow">"Afghanistan: A Country Study"</a>. <i>Country Studies</i>. U. S. Library of Congress (Federal Research Division). 150<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/aftoc.html" class="external free" title="http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/aftoc.html" rel="nofollow">http://lcweb2.loc.gov/frd/cs/aftoc.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-04-18</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Afghanistan%3A+A+Country+Study&amp;rft.atitle=Country+Studies&amp;rft.pages=150&amp;rft.pub=U.+S.+Library+of+Congress+%28Federal+Research+Division%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flcweb2.loc.gov%2Ffrd%2Fcs%2Faftoc.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Islam"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-146"><b><a href="#cite_ref-146" title="">^</a></b> See:
<ul>
