<li>J. A. Williams (1994), p.173</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book">"al-Ibāḍiyya". <i>Encyclopaedia of Islam Online</i>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=al-Ib%C4%81%E1%B8%8Diyya&amp;rft.atitle=Encyclopaedia+of+Islam+Online&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Islam"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
