<li><a href="http://www.islamicarchitecture.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.islamicarchitecture.org/" rel="nofollow">Islamic Architecture (IAORG)</a> illustrated descriptions and reviews of a large number of mosques, palaces, and monuments.</li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
